ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCanadian Food Inspection Agency - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving the ENTRY by the Canadian Food Inspection Agency into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA applicable to all employees of the Agency in the Scientific and Analytical Bargaining Unit, which provides for the changes to the previous Collective Agreement and which expires on September 30, 2018.
